      <title>印度农民拒绝政府提出的保证农作物价格的提议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/india-farmers-reject-government-offer-on-minimum-guaranteed-crop-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度农民团体拒绝了政府提出的保证某些目前没有此类保障的农作物最低价格的提议，预计周三将恢复正在进行的抗议活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/india-farmers-reject-government-offer-on-minimum-guaranteed-crop-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 06:31:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>报告称中国因劳工和财产问题引发抗议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/china-protests-due-to-labor-property-issues-rise-report-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一份新报告显示，去年年底中国的抗议活动数量不断增加，这加剧了试图推动经济反弹的官员的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/china-protests-due-to-labor-property-issues-rise-report-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 05:02:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京向喜爱豪华轿车的朝鲜领导人金正恩赠送新车</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/putin-gifts-new-car-to-north-korea-s-luxury-limo-loving-leader-kim</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京向这位热爱豪华轿车的朝鲜领导人赠送了一辆新车，这可能违反了联合国决议，他与金正恩的友好关系发生了新的转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/putin-gifts-new-car-to-north-korea-s-luxury-limo-loving-leader-kim</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 05:00:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗马尼亚可能需要在十年的剩余时间内减少预算赤字</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/romania-may-need-the-rest-of-the-decade-to-reduce-budget-deficit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗马尼亚可能需要在本世纪末将其预算赤字降至欧盟规则设定的目标，因为政府将在选举年应对公众对财政紧缩的抵制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/romania-may-need-the-rest-of-the-decade-to-reduce-budget-deficit</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国公司寻求在预算中分享亨特计划的选民减税计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/uk-plc-seeks-share-of-voter-tax-cuts-planned-by-hunt-in-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理里希·苏纳克和财政大臣杰里米·亨特长期以来一直表示，他们将下个月的预算视为优先为选民提供税收优惠的机会。尽管三个月前才从亨特所说的“有史以来最大的商业投资推动”措施中受益，但英国商界仍希望获得更多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/uk-plc-seeks-share-of-voter-tax-cuts-planned-by-hunt-in-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列考虑对 10 月 7 日袭击者进行艾希曼式公开审判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/israel-weighs-eichmann-style-public-trials-for-oct-7-attackers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[1961 年的四个多月里，大屠杀策划者阿道夫·艾希曼 (Adolf Eichmann) 坐在耶路撒冷临时法庭的防弹亭里，在摄像机呼呼作响的情况下，以反人类罪接受以色列国的审判。两年后，上诉失败后，他被绞死——该国历史上最后一次处决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/israel-weighs-eichmann-style-public-trials-for-oct-7-attackers</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国在联合国安理会文本草案中警告以色列不要袭击拉法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/us-warns-against-rafah-assault-and-calls-for-ceasefire-in-draft-un-text</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据彭博社看到的草案文本副本，美国提出了一项联合国安理会决议，警告以色列不要袭击加沙地带南部的拉法，并呼吁暂时停火。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/us-warns-against-rafah-assault-and-calls-for-ceasefire-in-draft-un-text</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 22:39:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国联邦调查局 (FBI) 和英国犯罪调查局称他们已经瓦解了 LockBit 团伙</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/fbi-uk-crime-agency-say-they-have-disrupted-lockbit-hacking-gang</link>
      <description><![CDATA[包括美国联邦调查局 (FBI) 和英国国家犯罪局在内的国际执法机构联盟表示，他们已经扰乱了有史以来最多产的黑客组织之一 LockBit，包括关闭该组织用于支付勒索软件的网站。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/fbi-uk-crime-agency-say-they-have-disrupted-lockbit-hacking-gang</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 22:17:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于制裁削弱了尼日尔的财政状况，尼日尔错过了三笔债券支付</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/niger-misses-24-2-million-debt-payments-as-sanctions-bite</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于去年政变后对尼日尔实施的制裁给国家财政带来压力，尼日尔又未能偿还三笔国内债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/niger-misses-24-2-million-debt-payments-as-sanctions-bite</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 20:47:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北京扩大经济控制，中国加强对科技的控制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/china-vows-to-centralize-tech-development-under-communist-party</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国执政的共产党将在引导其庞大的科技产业方面发挥更大的作用，这是北京打算对世界第二大经济体的大部分地区施加更大影响的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/china-vows-to-centralize-tech-development-under-communist-party</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 13:20:54 GMT</pubDate>
